<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Profile Update Required</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px;">
        <div
            style="background-color: #f44336; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;">
            <h1>Profile Update Required</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 20px 0;">
            <p>Thank you for submitting your profile for our MedicalHub platform. After careful review, our admin team
                has determined that some updates are required before we can approve your profile.</p>
            <!-- <p>The following areas need attention:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>[Specific reason 1]</li>
                <li>[Specific reason 2]</li>
                <li>[Specific reason 3]</li>
            </ul> -->
            <p>Please log in to your account and make the necessary updates. Once you've made the changes, your profile
                will be reviewed again.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= loginURL %>"
                    style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #f44336; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Update
                    Your Profile</a>
            </p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance with updating your profile, please don't hesitate to contact
                our support team.</p>
            <p>We appreciate your understanding and look forward to welcoming you to our MedicalHub platform once the
                required updates are completed.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>MedicalHub Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>